                    <li><strong>PASS:</strong> You have cleared all requirements for your Bachelor of Arts degree.</li>
                    <li><strong>SUPP:</strong> Supplementary (meaning you must retake one final year paper to graduate).</li>
                    <li><strong>RW:</strong> Result Withheld (usually due to missing previous year's marksheets in the university database).</li>
                    <li><strong>PBD:</strong> Previous Back Due (meaning you passed final year but still have papers from Part I or II to clear).</li>
